Hey there !
I am trying to filter the deals using api which is mentioned below. I want to fetch deals having closedate greater than equal to operator with  a specific timestamp.
but it's fetching all the deals.
Could you guys please help me fetch the required results . I have mentioned the JSON filter below.

```{
  "filterGroups": [
